Package bradleyross.opensource.jackcess

The Jackcess library is an open-source project written by Health Market Science to process Microsoft Access mdb files (Access 2000 format only).

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    helpers
    Static methods that are designed to aid in the use of the Jackcess software to read MDB files.
    thirdTest
    Reads an MDB file using the Microsoft Access 2000 format and displays information concerning its layout and contents.

Package bradleyross.opensource.jackcess Description

The Jackcess library is an open-source project written by Health Market Science to process Microsoft Access mdb files (Access 2000 format only). It has a Source Forge site containing the source code and binaries and is distributed under the GNU Lesser GPL (General Public License).
